              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Over the years, thousands of tour operators have trusted us to be part of their business. That trust is something we never take for granted.</p><p>Every booking made through a WP Travel Engine website represents a real business serving real travelers. Remembering that responsibility helps guide every decision we make.</p><p>Thank you for allowing us to be part of your journey. We look forward to continuing to build, improve, and grow alongside you.</p>",
